message: Prodam Akasa M.2 to PCIe adapter card.  Zraven pride original embalaža.  Slike na: https://www.bolha.com/razsiritvene-kart...  Convert M.2 SSD to work in main board PCIe x4 bus slot Designed for M.2 PCIe "M Key" SSD Support: 2230, 2242, 2260, 2280 and 22110 size PCIe SSD Material: metal bracket, printed circuit board Dimension: 148(L) x 120(W) x 21.7(H) mm Onboard LED indicators: Power - Blue / M.2 PCIe SSD Activity - Red (flashing) Product code: AK-PCCM2P-01  Cena: 10 Eur Sem iz LJ Menjave me ne zanimajo Več info na ZS
